rComments: A very pleasant and kind professor. There is a lot of material, so do not expect this to be an easy A. The grading criteria are clear, I usually found that my grade reflected the amount of work I put into it. Good for people who learn independently; but not a class for everyone.

If you think this is a bird course just turn around because Prof MacIsaac makes this class way harder than it has to be. Don't get me wrong, the material is quite interesting but the exam is hard and she makes you do these assignments that should be worth more than 3.3% each (seriously 5 pages for 3.3%?). She also teaches for 1hr before the midterm
